sg.edu.cs2103aug2015_w13_2j.ui

Class FeedbackMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • sg.edu.cs2103aug2015_w13_2j.ui.FeedbackMessage

  • public class FeedbackMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    FeedbackMessage class encapsulates the data necessary to display styled feedback messages to the user. It comprises a message string retrievable via getMessage() and a FeedbackMessage.FeedbackType object which determines the type of feedback as well as the styling.
    Author:
    Zhu Chunqi
